{"tid":2413421,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"中國科興疫苗擺明想借香港去對外宣傳","createTime":"2021-02-18T16:24:36.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-18T16:25:24.000Z","uid":25468,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"d04b45c5d8fb511462b5a0e2a6da5ab12e22e9c8","tid":2413421,"uid":25468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T16:24:36.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"xx-large\">疫苗接種計劃│首批科興疫苗明午抵港 5類人士優先接種</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n政府公布，首批100萬劑內地科興新型冠狀病毒疫苗，將於明天下午運抵本港；而德國製造的BioNTech疫苗，首批100萬劑預料本月底前運抵本港。 公務員事務局長聶德權公布，將有5類人士優先接種疫苗。 <br />\n<br />\n第一類：醫療機構人員，以及參與抗疫的工作人員； <br />\n<br />\n第二類：<strong><span class=\"limegreen\">60歲以上人士</span></strong>（陪同70歲以上長者接種疫苗的人士，都可獲安排打針，名額最多2人）； <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n第三類：安老及殘疾人士院舍的院友及員工； <br />\n<br />\n第四類：維持必要公共服務的人員，例如環境衛生的前線人員，包括處理廢物、污水、渠務及街市潔淨的人員等，或經常要與市民接觸的<span class=\"limegreen\">紀律部隊人員</span>，以及郵政前線人員等；<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n 第五類：跨境運輸口岸港口工作人員，例如跨境貨車司機、機組人員、機場、碼頭和陸路口岸人員、跨境船隻船員，以及跨境作業漁民。<br />\n<br />\n優先群組下周二起可網上預約接種<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/local/2379511/%E7%96%AB%E8%8B%97%E6%8E%A5%E7%A8%AE%E8%A8%88%E5%8A%83%E2%94%82%E9%A6%96%E6%89%B9%E7%A7%91%E8%88%88%E7%96%AB%E8%8B%97%E6%98%8E%E5%8D%88%E6%8A%B5%E6%B8%AF-5%E9%A1%9E%E4%BA%BA%E5%A3%AB%E5%84%AA%E5%85%88%E6%8E%A5%E7%A8%AE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Flocal%2F2379511%2F%25E7%2596%25AB%25E8%258B%2597%25E6%258E%25A5%25E7%25A8%25AE%25E8%25A8%2588%25E5%258A%2583%25E2%2594%2582%25E9%25A6%2596%25E6%2589%25B9%25E7%25A7%2591%25E8%2588%2588%25E7%2596%25AB%25E8%258B%2597%25E6%2598%258E%25E5%258D%2588%25E6%258A%25B5%25E6%25B8%25AF-5%25E9%25A1%259E%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E5%25A3%25AB%25E5%2584%25AA%25E5%2585%2588%25E6%258E%25A5%25E7%25A8%25AE&d=ffZD4KHswvQdDnqC%2BKe69MjT01h1KCp2%2Bw2KB0oDRGE%3D&h=2f8586b7\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/local/2379511/%E7%96%AB%E8%8B%97%E6%8E%A5%E7%A8%AE%E8%A8%88%E5%8A%83%E2%94%82%E9%A6%96%E6%89%B9%E7%A7%91%E8%88%88%E7%96%AB%E8%8B%97%E6%98%8E%E5%8D%88%E6%8A%B5%E6%B8%AF-5%E9%A1%9E%E4%BA%BA%E5%A3%AB%E5%84%AA%E5%85%88%E6%8E%A5%E7%A8%AE</a>"},{"pid":"57d4f0f91c4d9f68448ef0d4470c1269aeedfa58","tid":2413421,"uid":25468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T16:25:24.000Z","msg":"應該9 成人都登記打 BioNTech <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}